high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the fridge. Turn right again to go to the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Place the pan inside the fridge. Chill then take it out.
Turn to the  left and walk around the counter to the left.
Place the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan and take it out of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and veer right to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front left burner.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pan in the fridge on the same self as the yellow cup, to the left and in front of it. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left, take a few steps, and turn left again to get the outside count near the pot.
Place the pan on the counter to the right of the pot.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on a counter.

high_descs: Walk to the stove on the other side of the room.
Pick up the pan from the front left burner on the stove.
Turn around and walk straight to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the pan on the top shelf of the fridge to the left of the yellow mug, close the door, open the door, pick up the pan, close the door.
Walk around to the other side of the counter.
Put the pan down on the counter to the right of the cauldron.
anns.task_desc: To chill a pan and put it down on the counter.
